---
title: Persian-Inspired Chickpea, Carrot and Chicken Stew with Toasted Garlic Flatbread
description: Tender Middle Eastern-spiced carrots are the star of this warming tomato-based stew. Toasted almonds and a spicy chili-garlic sauce are the perfect toppers for this crave-worthy dinner!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/ragout-de-pois-chiches-de-carottes-et-de-poitrines-de-poulet-a-la-perse-9092c51b.jpg
